{"tid":1672677,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國將舉辦2021新版世冠盃","createTime":"2019-10-24T08:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T10:47:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"10b2eeedd261c516f9845e9bc9692a0c4ab887c7","tid":1672677,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】FIFA主席恩芬天奴周四宣佈，首屆改制後的世界冠軍球會盃將於2021年在中國舉行，是國內首次承辦國際足協旗下的成年男子足球世界賽。<br />\n<br />\n「這是足球的歷史時刻！」FIFA主席恩芬天奴（Gianni Infantino）周四在上海宣佈中國將舉辦2021年世界冠軍球會盃時高呼。「世上每個喜歡足球的人都會十分期待賽事的來臨。」<br />\n<br />\n早前，國際足協已落實從2021年開始，世冠盃的參賽名額將由7個大幅擴展至24支球隊角逐，並改為每4年舉辦一次，以取代過往在世界盃年前舉行的洲際國家盃。據報，改制後的世冠盃將包括8支歐洲球隊，6支南美洲球隊，亞洲、非洲、中北美洲則各3支球隊，餘下1隊就是來自大洋洲的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n然而，2019年及2020年的世冠盃仍會按現時規模在卡塔爾舉行，讓這個2022年世界盃主辦國能好好測試場地及基礎設施，以順利承辦這項國際足協的旗艦級賽事。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"fcf27ce68240ce65fc8504c557721707902e7fb1","tid":1672677,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-fec4731f02e1aee6b860d38013cb3f19_hd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-fec4731f02e1aee6b860d38013cb3f19_hd.gif&h=08c775b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c0c426eb4666fd57d80baedac6c1748bff99b94","tid":1672677,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/63ae9093ee08476cb253a4b96b160c45\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F63ae9093ee08476cb253a4b96b160c45&h=f8a73d4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf05b2e311aa77846d778c9c2ef190c136c0c6a9","tid":1672677,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"以為世界冠軍球會盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaa84f913d984fb68569d5a1994d2b983e8fb75","tid":1672677,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedB